reviewText: Had seen this one on Hallmark years ago but only after it was well into it. Liked what I had seen but always wanted to see it from the beginning.  It's a great lesson in true friendship and all things are not as they seem. Get your tissues ready, great movie!
Title: Ladies of the House

reviewText: Ladies Of The House is very entertaining.  3 ladies remodel a house as a church project.  Donna Mills was especially good in her scenes.  A well done film that makes some good points about how much you can do if you try.
Title: Ladies of the House
